
<h2 class="text-center title">About TrakStats</h2>
<br />
<hr />
<br /><br /><br />
<div class="col-xs-12">
  <div class="col-xs-5">
    <h3 class="text-center">Overview</h3>
    <p class="text-center">-------------------</p>
    <p class="info">
      TrakStats is a simple way to track stats from your round of golf.  If you have tried to keep track of
      your stats in the past and have failed, look no further!  When you post a score, it will be displayed to other members on the home page.
      You have access to a user dashboard, "My Stats", which lets you look at your stats in-depth.
      Each round you post will be tracked and you can see all of your averages. Rounds will track:
    </p>
    <br />
    <ul class="info">
      <li>Scoring Average</li>
      <li>Fwy's hit %</li>
      <li>Green's hit %</li>
      <li>Putting / Putts Per Round Average</li>
      <li>Total Birdies</li>
      <li>Total Pars</li>
    </ul>
    <br />
    <p class="info">
      You also have access to the following:
    </p>
    <ul class="info">
      <li>Round Edits (click your score from 'My Stats')</li>
      <li>Course Yardage Calculator</li>
      <li>View other member rounds from the main page (click their score)</li>
      <li>Ranking page to compare stats with other members (Premium Members Only  - <%= link_to 'Upgrade!', premium_path, class: 'links2' %>)</li>
      <li>Leave comments or messages for friends!</li>
    </ul>


  </div>
